  "description": "A wide-angle scenic view featuring a portion of a steel bridge structure in the foreground, transitioning to a calm body of water, and culminating in a distant view of snow-capped mountains under a blue sky dotted with fluffy white clouds. The bridge is a dark grey, creating a strong contrast with the brighter natural elements. The mountains are silhouetted against the sky, indicating distance. The water surface reflects some of the sky's color. The overall impression is one of vastness and tranquility.",
